1. The Trump administration strengthens the status of Bitcoin, and Altcoins face regulatory uncertainty;
2. IMF: El Salvador has not defaulted on its increased Bitcoin holdings, and the loan agreement is expected to take effect on April 30;
3. Ansem: Ye has a global influence to promote the popularization of cryptocurrencies;
4. Jupiter is about to launch a new verification system to enhance community participation;
5. Conic Finance of the Curve Finance ecosystem announced that it would stop operations, and LPs need to withdraw funds as soon as possible;
6. The author of "Rich Dad Poor Dad": The stock market crash crisis has arrived, and it is recommended to invest in real Bitcoin, gold and silver;
7. Mysten Labs announced the acquisition of game development platform Parasol.
